file.name: api-spec-v3.0.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  title: Application API
  description: Application API Specification.
  version: 1.0.0

paths:
  /services/users:
    get:
      summary: Returns a list of users.
      description: Returns a list of all available users.
      responses:
        '200':
          description: A JSON array of Users
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: array
                items:
                  $ref: '#/components/schemas/User'
  /services/user:
    post:
      summary: Create User.
      description: Create new user.
      responses:
        '200':
          description: User created.
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/User'
      requestBody:
        required: true
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/CreateUser'
  /services/users/{userId}:
    delete:
      summary: Delete User.
      description: Delete existing user.
      responses:
        '200':
          description: User deleted.
      parameters:
        - in: path
          name: userId
          required: true
          schema:
            type: string


components:
  schemas:
    User:
      properties:
        id:
          type: string
        name:
          type: string
        email:
          type: string
        enabled:
          type: boolean
      required:
        - id
        - name
        - email
        - enabled
    CreateUser:
      properties:
        name:
          type: string
        email:
          type: string
        enabled:
          type: boolean
      required:
        - name
        - email
        - enabled
